high_descs: Turn and go to where the lap top is on the coffee table.
Pick up the watch that is on the left corner of the coffee table.
Turn to your left facing the two chairs and go to the table to the left of the chairs while holding the watch in your hand.
Place the watch on the table next to the chair in front of the lamp.
Turn around and go to the opposite side of the coffee table.
Pick up the watch that is on the table.
With the watch in hand turn and go to the table to the left of the two chairs.
Place the watch in front of the lamp on the table.
anns.task_desc: Move two watches to the table next to the chairs.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and walk up to the coffee table.
Pick up the watch off of the left side of the coffee table.
Turn around and walk towards the door, then turn right and walk over to the round black table in the corner of the room.
Put the watch on the round black table.
Turn around and walk back over to the coffee table.
Pick up the watch off of the coffee table.
Turn left and walk forward, then hang a right and walk back up to the round black table in the corner of the room.
Put the watch on the round black table.
anns.task_desc: Move two watches to a round black table.

high_descs: go to the coffee table with the computer on it
pick up the watch sitting by the computer on the coffee table
go to the end table with the light on it
set the watch on the table
go back to the coffee table
pick up the other watch on the coffee table
go back to the end table
set the watch down with the other watch
anns.task_desc: move both watches to the end table
